@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wlimza(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.49)) - ((v2 + 0.74 + tmp + 0.11) / (tmp + 0.20 - v1 + 0.29)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.62) - (v1 + 0.72 - v2 + 0.99)) - (0.20 / (v0 + 0.55 / v1 + 0.87)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
